{"tid":483032,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"欅坂46交流區第四十一回:菅井友香お誕生日おめでとう🎉","createTime":"2017-11-28T17:29:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-28T17:35:26.000Z","uid":1986,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ced5795d2aa11ca0b3a281f75ddc8b638741190b","tid":483032,"uid":1986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T17:29:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">人見人愛守屋茜生日快樂!!!🎉</span></strong></div></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/s3fiXgL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs3fiXgL.gif&h=d64e4a3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/kIW7mlj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FkIW7mlj.gif&h=95dc42fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/jX7n78H.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FjX7n78H.gif&h=703830aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/xvQJaUW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FxvQJaUW.gif&h=f3eb09e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/020230_b9331b514fb885b933e889c2825caf75.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F020230_b9331b514fb885b933e889c2825caf75.gif&h=e7566900&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">欅坂46(Keyakizaka46)是日本大型女子偶像組合乃木坂46的姐妹組合</span>，製作人同樣為秋元康。組合名字中的「46」讀作「Forty-six／フォーティシックス」，而不是讀作「四十六／よんじゅうろく」。2016年4月6日，欅坂46出道單曲《サイレントマジョリティー》販售，首週銷量達261,580枚，除了登上Oricon週榜首位，還同時刷新歷代女性藝人銷量最高的出道單曲。同年5月8日，在SHOWROOM公布平假名欅坂46的合格成員。2016年12月31日，首次登場NHK紅白歌合戰。 <br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.keyakizaka46.com/img/14/diar/88/mem/member/sub-member-6897_jpg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.keyakizaka46.com%2Fimg%2F14%2Fdiar%2F88%2Fmem%2Fmember%2Fsub-member-6897_jpg.jpg&h=c3ef22e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">成員名單</span></span><br />\n<br />\n欅坂46<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/bK1naOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FbK1naOV.jpg&h=d95d6bb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nけやき坂46 (ひらがなけやき)<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/gglDffE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FgglDffE.jpg&h=8c67622d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/014743_335e53af72e710eeffa2720180384abb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F014743_335e53af72e710eeffa2720180384abb.jpg&h=1c8fd2e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">5thシングル『風に吹かれても』発売中</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/015108_aed472fe8ec92b7bc36c5dbb674c033c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F015108_aed472fe8ec92b7bc36c5dbb674c033c.jpg&h=bba9a88f&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">けやき坂46主演連続ドラマ「Re:Mind」2017年10月19日より毎週木曜午前0:59〜（水曜深夜）日本テレビにて放送スタート！</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">【成員有幾靚女？】我直接用例子答你。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/012822_fa0f4a7853be10595b2d0a0990c74b45.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F012822_fa0f4a7853be10595b2d0a0990c74b45.jpg&h=5a42a397&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/012822_a4f1189a8ab05c57efec5dc097f021c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F012822_a4f1189a8ab05c57efec5dc097f021c5.jpg&h=5924848f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/012824_f655f4754b9b3cafed6584ce2fbc0dcf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F012824_f655f4754b9b3cafed6584ce2fbc0dcf.jpg&h=80740d92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/012824_74d27f2355742f2596a491d187dac336.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F012824_74d27f2355742f2596a491d187dac336.jpg&h=36b806c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/012824_b0048278a0767fef3eecf5eb320c6e32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F012824_b0048278a0767fef3eecf5eb320c6e32.jpg&h=16619b1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/012824_12e1740ddcaa7f02b44d812c354e5627.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F012824_12e1740ddcaa7f02b44d812c354e5627.jpg&h=946f5158&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/012824_7562160079534bf247c8cdedc9a5c289.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F012824_7562160079534bf247c8cdedc9a5c289.jpg&h=f242f26e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">歡迎新人加入</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://keyakizaka46style.com/sort/keyakizaka46sort.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkeyakizaka46style.com%2Fsort%2Fkeyakizaka46sort.html&d=Mu1uKurn9zdcSqIMyEx0GDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=fac7ecb6\" target=\"_blank\">http://keyakizaka46style.com/sort/keyakizaka46sort.html</a></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請新/舊手足定期體檢，以便加入DD黨</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Q&amp;A</div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n1）欅坂46乃何許人也？ <br />\n簡單來說，欅坂46是來自日本的偶像組合，演戲唱歌跳舞等全部都會參與，是正統全能型偶像。 <br />\n<br />\n2）那裡可以購買欅坂46既有關產品（生寫、CD、海報、寫真集、演唱會等）？ <br />\n一般來說，信和地庫會有存貨，不過價錢就...另外有不少商品需於官方WEBSHOP/會場購入，不過這裡有機會提供代購，要看看手足們的心情。 <br />\n<br />\n3）這裡可否討論坂道以外的組合？ <br />\n不可。皆因這裡主要討論欅坂46，你也可作理性討論，攻擊、黑其他成員(禾ru除外)，但請先作好世界大戰的準備。 <br />\n<br />\n4）那麼我要如何見到欅坂46成員？ <br />\n直接飛去日本參加握手會、演唱會，不要幻想他們來港舉辦握手會，因為此舉極為傻豬。詳細辦法請向手足查詢。 <br />\n<br />\n5) 呢度大佬係? <br />\n沒有<br />\n<br />\n6）會員舞木香純是咪HIHI？<br />\n是。因為三槍為人臭串、極度無恥，自然會引起其他手足責罵他。雖然佢犯禁逼走不少手足，但因他臉皮極厚，罵極不走真是無可奈何。 <br />\n<br />\n7）除了坂道46系，有什麼值得推薦？<br />\n咁撚正重洗鬼睇其他咩<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">TEMPLATE:</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1fBDpfFnmtje6HvysvE3GQPi4ZdnuY9oaF6NnpesCD0U/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1fBDpfFnmtje6HvysvE3GQPi4ZdnuY9oaF6NnpesCD0U%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=Mu1uKurn9zdcSqIMyEx0GDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=8b779321\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1fBDpfFnmtje6HvysvE3GQPi4ZdnuY9oaF6NnpesCD0U/edit?usp=sharing</a>"},{"pid":"8b470c5ee1d0d411fcb2a40e8b1cb7391adda1fb","tid":483032,"uid":34900,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T17:33:20.000Z","msg":"禾僕人菅井友香生日快樂<img s